{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"S1 LIVE VERIFICATION COMPLETE (against running Gerrit 3.14.1, 2026-07-02). All ACs met:\n\nAC1 (copyCondition applied + accepted): pushed project.config to refs/meta/config (16f8240, then f8bd6ac). Read-back via REST GET /projects/rebar/labels/LLM-Review -> copy_condition = 'changekind:NO_CODE_CHANGE OR changekind:MERGE_FIRST_PARENT_UPDATE' (Gerrit ACCEPTED the token; T1 resolved — no silent drop). Verified label copy_condition = 'changekind:NO_CODE_CHANGE' (deliberate divergence: LLM-Review carries on re-merge, Verified re-runs).\n\nAC2 (submit type recorded before pin; pin in quiet window): pre-pin record captured earlier (MERGE_IF_NECESSARY inherited). Quiet window established by abandoning 3 stale e2e probes (162/62/61) -> 0 open changes on main before push. Post-pin: use_content_merge configured_value flipped INHERIT->TRUE (proves [submit] block landed); submit_type = MERGE_IF_NECESSARY.\n\nAC3 (group exists w/ ACLs; setup-project.sh idempotent): created feature-branch-drivers group (UUID 3fe3138810fb101edd4e3b6b26fb4b9318d7f120; members=[JoeOakhartNava], includes=[Administrators]). setup-project.sh extended to create+converge the group; ran it live (registered a temp SSH key, since removed): DRY_RUN reported 'group already exists' + 'refs/meta/config already up to date (no-op)' == idempotent convergence proven.\n\nAC4/AC5 (ADR + docs): ADR docs/adr/0025-feature-branch-merge-carry.md (amends 0013, 0020) — merge-carry rationale, Verified/LLM-Review divergence, membership policy, copyCondition back-out + group RETIRE path. docs/gerrit-aws-setup.md gained section 6a.\n\nAC6 (LIVE negative checks):\n- feature/* creation by non-member (rebar-review-bot, Service Users, not in group): PUT branch -> HTTP 403 'not permitted: create on refs/heads/feature/...'. Member (JoeOakhartNava) -> 201 created. \n- merge push by non-member: first attempt exposed that All-Projects grants pushMerge on refs/for/* to Registered Users, so the additive rule did NOT restrict. FIX: added exclusiveGroupPermissions=pushMerge on both refs/for/refs/heads/{main,feature/*} (overrides inherited grant). Re-test: bot merge push -> 'you are not allowed to upload merges' (REFUSED); member merge push -> SUCCESS. \n\nE5 (submit-strategy actually merges, not just parses): change 184 -> admin-voted LLM-Review+1 & Verified+1 -> submittable -> submitted -> status MERGED via merge-if-necessary. \n\nCleanup: all test changes abandoned; test branches deleted; temp SSH key removed; 0 leftover artifacts."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783056418295105001,"uuid":"c8f5ca09-a30b-4d02-8638-834f3e52ad7d"}